 \dfrac{d}{dt} \Big(\vec{b}(t)\Big) = \lambda(\vec{a}(t) - \vec{b}(t))
 \dfrac{d}{dt} \Big(x\hat{i} + y\hat{j}\Big) = \lambda((ut-x)\hat{i} - y\hat{j})
